list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment:
Bugfix authenticatedFetch queryparams in path
For arbitrary-page calls, the query parameters are part of the path and must be handled accordingly. Therefore, the query parameter filterer only fires if `!api`.

task.summary: Made transcluded icon on all transcluded:yes pages

Added Upgrade Containers to API Dashboard
Converts to the new content containers

Compile button mac/safari fix
Fixed issue due to how safari scopes variables.
Added Toggle Switch for New<==>Edit Remix

bundled dynamicIndexMaker.js
-wrapped dynamicIndexMaker.js in self-invoking function -changed var to let/const -formatted file -still has type coercion issues

JSON-ified libraries
Allows library object in reuse.js to be parsed as if it was JSON
Updated cleanPath to be less aggressive
Forker changed from Cross-Library to LibreBot

Moved & consolidated createBundle.js to /Miscellaneous.
Now we can all share the createBundle.js code to compile React.
Bugfix nodePrint.js being crawled by GoogleBot

Initial NewReactTemplate
A starting template for new React projects. Involves React Hooks.
